EuroCham is delighted to invite you to this interactive dialogue with the HCMC Tax Authority where the latest relating news and changes will be given an update as well as your questions and concerns on taxation issues will be directly answered.

Some main issues to be discussed:

Latest tax laws and reforms taking effect in 2016 (PIT, CIT, VAT, Special Consumption tax, Import Duties, Transfer pricing and the Advanced Pricing Arrangement programme...)
Possible tax changes / new policies in 2016.
Direct interaction regarding tax related issues.